Foreign buyers will have to pay higher stamp duty when buying property in the UK and the extra cash will be used to help the homeless, according to the new Tory plans.
This move will neutralize the success of Corbyn's attempt to attract young voters
Stamp duty will be levied on those who do not pay taxes in the UK
